      • extractPossibleMatch

        private static <T> T extractPossibleMatch(java.util.Queue<T> checkedQueue,
                                          PlayerBuilding.QueueElementChecker<T> elementCheker)
        Function for extracting an element from the provided Queue that matches the all QueueElementCheckers conditions.
        Parameters:
        checkedQueue - the Queue that is being looked at.
        elementCheker - the conditions that an element of the Queue must fulfill.
        Returns:
        an element that fulfills either all conditions of the QueueElementChecker or null if none is found and the Queue was cycled through once.

      • addExtraAddonContendedTilePositions

        private void addExtraAddonContendedTilePositions()
        Function for adding the extra TilePositions to the contended ones that represent the default Position of the addon. This is needed since no other building is allowed to block any addons from being constructed which might happen if the space is not reserved.
